# Security Policy

## Supported Versions

| Version | Supported |
| ------- | --------- |
| Latest  | ✅         |
| Older   | ❌         |

## Reporting a Vulnerability

If you discover a security vulnerability, please report it through **GitHub**'s private vulnerability [reporting system](https://gitlab.com/kickr-dev/engine/security/advisories/new).
